Here are a few suggestions to keep your activewear performing and looking it’s best for years to come. Hand wash or machine wash items alone or with like colors and fabrics. Turn items that are embellished inside out to wash. When machine-washing it is best to use a gentle cycle and always wash in cool water with a mild soap.
